== How to build MacSim ==

=== Requirement ===

  SCons

  * How to get SCons
    Ubuntu --> apt-get install scons


=== Build steps ===

  ./build.py


=== Build options ===

  -j (--thread) : specify number of threads for parallel build
  -d : debug build
  -p : gprof build
  -c : clean
  --dramsim : using DRAMSim2
  --power : using EnergyIntrospector for power model
          (Please note that power model is currently available to only internal developers.)


=== Build outcome ===

  bin/macsim


